                       Crow/Northern Cheyenne Hospital
   MISSION STATEMENT

   The mission of the Crow/Northern Cheyenne Service Unit is to work in
   partnership with the people we serve to elevate their physical, mental,
   social and spiritual health to the highest level. Our vision statement
   is We believe a Healthy Population exists through a creative and
   innovative health care system driven by the health care needs
   established cooperatively with those we serve.


